level.heading: Editor's Notes
level.text: Former § 8-2204 has been recodified as § 8-2034.

The Budget Director of the Council of the District of Columbia has determined, as of February 15, 2012, that the fiscal effect of Law 18-289 has not been included in an approved budget and financial plan. Therefore, the provisions of sections 5 through 10 of Law 18-289 are not in effect.
